OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe odd
OL,6,Fshower possible in the evening but
OL,7,Fmainly dry with late bright or sunny
OL,8,Fspells. Turning cloudier overnight
OL,9,Fwith rain spreading eastwards before
OL,10,Fdawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain, heavy at times. Rain most
OL,14,Fpersistent in the morning, patchier
OL,15,Ffor a time in the afternoon. Brighter
OL,16,Fspells and some heavier rain possible
OL,17,Fagain later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
